{'product': 'Personalized Leather Journal', 'description': "The Personalized Leather Journal is a beautiful and functional gift that can be used for years to come. It's made from 100% full-grain leather, which is the highest quality leather available. The leather is soft and durable, and it will develop a beautiful patina over time. 

The journal is refillable, so you can replace the notebook as needed. It also has a leather loop inside the clasp to securely hold your pen. 

You can personalize the journal by submitting your own design to be engraved on the cover. This makes it a unique and special gift for any occasion.", 'uniqueAttributes': {'Personalized': 'Customers can add a personal touch by submitting their own design to be beautifully engraved on the cover.', 'Premium quality and outstanding craftsmanship': 'The journal is meticulously crafted from top-quality, thick leather, ensuring durability and longevity. It features a leather loop inside the clasp to securely hold your pen, making it convenient for writing on the go.', 'Refillable design': "The journal's refillable design allows you to replace the notebook as needed, ensuring that you can continue to use your personalized cover for years to come.", 'Full-grain leather': 'The journal is made from 100% full-grain leather, which is the highest quality leather available. It is durable, soft, and will develop a beautiful patina over time.'}}

{'product': 'Custom Name Bracelet with Curb Chain', 'description': 'This bracelet features a beautiful curb chain with personalized nameplate, creating the perfect gift for any special occasion. The personalization options allow you the freedom to customize your bracelet with the names of your loved ones, making it a truly unique and unforgettable piece of jewelry.

