{'product': 'Dainty Name Necklace', 'description': "This necklace is a stunning and personalized accessory, perfect for showing off your unique style. Whether it's family, friends, or special someones, you can wear their names proudly in this beautifully crafted piece.

The necklace is made from high quality solid 925 sterling silver and comes in a variety of finishes (sterling silver, 18K gold, or rose gold). It is also available in different lengths, so you can choose the perfect fit for your style.

Each necklace is custom-made by hand in the seller's workshop, ensuring attention to detail and a personal touch. You can specify the names and font number you want for your necklace, making it a truly unique and meaningful piece of jewelry.", 'uniqueAttributes': {'Customizable': 'With its multiple name design, this necklace allows customers to personalize it with names of their choice, making it a unique and meaningful piece of jewelry.', 'High-quality materials': 'The necklace is made from high-quality solid 925 sterling silver, ensuring durability and longevity. This sets it apart from generic necklaces that may use cheaper or less durable materials.', 'Handmade with care': "Each necklace is custom-made by hand in the seller's workshop, adding a personal touch and ensuring attention to detail. This is not commonly found in mass-produced generic necklaces.", 'Versatile design': 'The necklace is available in different finishes (sterling silver, 18K gold, or rose gold) and can be ordered in various lengths. This versatility allows customers to choose the perfect fit and style for their preferences.', 'Personalized service': 'The seller offers personalized service, allowing customers to specify the names and font number they want for their necklace. This level of customization is not typically found with generic necklaces.'}}

