{'product': 'Dainty Gold Birthstone Necklace in Cube', 'description': "This exquisite Birthstone Necklace is a meaningful and personalized gift, featuring a carefully selected gemstone that represents the birth month of the wearer. The pendant is delicately set in a Sterling Silver setting, adding a touch of elegance and refinement.

Choose from an array of birthstone options, each with its unique color and symbolism. Whether it's the deep blue of sapphire for September, the rich red of garnet for January, or the lush green of emerald for May, there's a birthstone that resonates with every individual.

The necklace is made from 925 Sterling Silver, ensuring durability and resistance to tarnishing. It is available in a range of lengths, from 14 inches to 24 inches, allowing the wearer to choose the perfect length for their personal style. The necklace comes with a stylish gift box, making it ready to be gifted to a loved one or to treat yourself.", 'uniqueAttributes': {'Personalized': 'Each necklace is customized with a birthstone that represents the birth month of the wearer, making it a meaningful and unique gift.', 'High-quality materials': 'The necklace is made from 925 Sterling Silver, which is known for its durability and resistance to tarnishing, ensuring that the necklace will last for years to come.', 'Delicate design': 'The pendant is delicately set in a Sterling Silver setting, creating a piece of jewelry that is both elegant and refined. This sets it apart from generic necklaces that may have a more bulky or less refined design.', 'Versatile length': 'The necklace is available in a range of lengths, from 14 inches to 24 inches, allowing the wearer to choose the perfect length for their personal style and preferences.', 'Thoughtful packaging': 'The necklace comes with a stylish gift box, making it ready to be gifted to a loved one or to treat yourself.'}}

{'product': 'Multi-Location Wedding Anniversary Print', 'description': 'This A4 Met Engaged Married Foil Map Print allows for customization with three favorite locations, a meaningful title, and personalized text, making it a unique and thoughtful gift. Each print is handmade, giving it a unique and artisanal quality that cannot be replicated by mass-produced items. 

Customers can choose from a selection of paper and foil colors to match their personal style and home decor. A preview is provided for customer approval before production, ensuring satisfaction with the final product. 

The print can be framed or unframed, and the size can be customized to fit different spaces. This flexibility allows customers to tailor the print to their specific needs and preferences. The print serves as a keepsake of special locations and memories, making it a meaningful and personal gift.', 'uniqueAttributes': {'Personalized': 'This print allows for customization with three favorite locations, a meaningful title, and personalized text, making it a unique and thoughtful gift.', 'Handmade': 'Each print is handmade, giving it a unique and artisanal quality that cannot be replicated by mass-produced items.', 'Choice of colors': 'Customers can choose from a selection of paper and foil colors to match their personal style and home décor.', 'Preview': 'A preview is provided for customer approval before production, ensuring satisfaction with the final product.', 'Flexibility': 'The print can be framed or unframed, and the size can be customized to fit different spaces. This flexibility allows customers to tailor the print to their specific needs and preferences.', 'Sentimental value': 'The print serves as a keepsake of special locations and memories, making it a meaningful and personal gift.'}}

{'product': 'Personalized Night Light', 'description': 'Our homemade lights are the perfect gift for your loved ones. Whether it’s for Christmas, Valentine’s Day, Father’s Day, Mother’s Day, Birthdays, Weddings, or any other event, our lights are fit for the occasion! 

The lights are made from sustainable materials, making them a more environmentally friendly choice. They are also handmade with care in Canada, ensuring that they are of the highest quality and that they are made to last.

You can choose from different sizes, shapes, and colors to create a personalized gift that is perfect for the recipient. You can also add a personal touch by engraving a name, date, or special message on the acrylic or wood. This makes it a truly unique and meaningful keepsake.', 'uniqueAttributes': {'Customization': 'Our lights are highly customizable. You can choose from different sizes, shapes, and colors to create a personalized gift that is perfect for the recipient.', 'Personalization': 'Add a personal touch to your gift by engraving a name, date, or special message on the acrylic or wood. This makes it a truly unique and meaningful keepsake.', 'Handmade in Canada': 'Our lights are handmade with care in Canada. This ensures that they are of the highest quality and that they are made to last.', 'Eco-friendly': 'Our lights are made from sustainable materials, making them a more environmentally friendly choice.', 'Fast shipping': 'We prepare and ship your products in 1 or 2 business days. This means that you can get your gift in time for that special occasion.'}}

{'product': 'Personalized Mahjong Bag', 'description': 'This charming personalized multi functional mahjong game bag keeps all your essential mahjong winnings neatly contained. Featuring mahjong tiles and your name, this personalized game bag makes a perfect addition to any mahjong lovers game room, and makes a great gift for anyone who loves to play mahjong!

The mahjong bag is made of a machine-washable light-beige polyester-cotton blend that has a textured linen or soft canvas/burlap feel. The bag measures 9.25" W x 6" H and has a black zipper closure on top. The personalization is done with a method that puts the image inside the fabric so you do not feel the design and allows the pencil bag to stay super soft. The image is only on one side of the bag.

Due to the personalized nature of this item, we are not able to accept returns unless the item is damaged.', 'uniqueAttributes': {'Personalized': "The bag can be personalized with the recipient's name, making it a unique and thoughtful gift.", 'Multi-functional': 'The bag is not just for mahjong, it can be used for storing other items such as pencils, makeup, or travel accessories.', 'Durable': 'The bag is made of a machine-washable poly-cotton blend that has a textured linen and soft canvas feel, making it durable and easy to care for.', 'Soft and comfortable': 'The image is embedded in the fabric so the entire bag stays soft, ensuring a comfortable feel when handling.', 'Locally printed': 'The bag is printed and shipped from a facility in Houston, TX, supporting local businesses and reducing shipping times.'}}

{'product': 'Barware Gift Set', 'description': "The Barware Gift Set is an ideal gift for men, perfect for occasions such as Father's Day, birthdays, or as a gift for groomsmen. It includes a personalized whiskey decanter and matching glasses, making it a unique and thoughtful present. 

The decanter is made of high-quality glass and features a heavy, solid base that prevents it from tipping over easily. It has a capacity of 28oz (850ml), allowing it to hold a generous amount of whiskey or other spirits. The matching glasses each hold 250ml, making them perfect for enjoying a drink with friends or family.

The decanter can be personalized with the recipient's name, initials, or a special message, adding a personal touch to the gift. The set also comes with an optional wood display box, adding a touch of elegance and making it a more presentable gift.", 'uniqueAttributes': {'Customizable': 'The decanter can be personalized with the name of the recipient, making it a unique and thoughtful gift.', 'Heavy and solid base': 'Unlike many lightweight decanters, this one has a heavy, solid base that adds stability and prevents it from tipping over easily.', 'Large capacity': 'The decanter can hold up to 28oz (850ml) of liquid, making it ideal for storing and serving generous amounts of whiskey or other spirits.', 'Matching glasses': 'The set includes two matching glasses, allowing the recipient to enjoy their favorite drinks in style.', 'Upgraded wood display box': 'For an additional cost, the set can be upgraded to include a wood display box, adding a touch of elegance and making it a more presentable gift.'}}
